  "title": "如何更新手环版本和APP版本？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt; line-height:normal\">升级前，请确保手环和手机通过蓝牙正常连接。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt; line-height:normal\">更新手环版本：在APP中点击左上角设置图标，点击“更新荣耀手环 zero”，手环将会检测版本信息并更新。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt; line-height:normal\" align=\"center\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084807170001.png)</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt; line-height:normal\"> </p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt; line-height:normal\">更新APP版本：在APP中点击右上角小人图标，点击“关于”-“App版本更新”，当手机显示“更新...”时，即可检测APP版本信息并更新。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt; line-height:normal\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084807283002.png)</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;line-height:normal; text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\">**说明：**</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;line-height:normal; text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\">更新时，手环会自动断开蓝牙，请您耐心等待直至升级结束。</p>",
